  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A battle-worn cape, stolen from notorious pirate faction <span class=\"name name-special\">The Blight</span>. Woven from chemically-dipped nano-fibres, the fabric is completely impervious to the heat produced by jetpack exhaust.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一件专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>一件从臭名昭著的<span class=\"name name-special\">瘟疫</span>海盗派系那里偷来的披风，表面战痕累累。由化学浸渍的纳米纤维编织而成，面料完全不受喷气背包排气产生的热量影响。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>一件經歷多次戰鬥而磨損的披風，從惡名昭彰的海盜陣營<span class=\"name name-special\">「毀滅」</span>竊取而來。由浸泡過化學物質的奈米纖維編織而成，可以完全隔絕噴射背包廢氣所產生的熱量。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>裡改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
